title: PM Malcolm Turnbull 'more receptive' on issue, campaigner Dr Philip Nitschke says
text: Voluntary euthanasia campaigner Philip Nitschke believes Prime Minister Malcolm Turnbull will be more receptive than his predecessor to a proposal to remove laws that ended legal assisted suicide in the NT. ...
